    "created_at": "2022-03-31T19:49:04Z",
    "updated_at": "2022-03-31T20:04:52Z",
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Converting this repo into a monorepo (with all controllers placed into their own package) is now a goal of the newly established core team and it is something we will be aiming to complete by end of Q2.\r\n\r\nAs it relates to the discussion above, we have decided that we do not want to synchronize versions among all of the packages in this repo. Eventually, this repo will be renamed `core` and will house other packages which are not related to controllers. We want to be able to give ourselves and product teams the independence to maintain packages with as little coupling as possible.\r\n\r\nConsult [this document](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1G3M-lcwvfNFs3Tq4lVzhywqzYhCqPqBN7c5n8TC9sWM/edit) for more information on our plan going forward.",
